Source: multiply.js

/**
 * Multiples a and b.
 * @function multiply
 * @param {integer} a - 1st Number.
 * @param {integer} b - 2nd Number.
 * @returns {number} The product of `a` and `b`.
 */
function multiply(a, b) {
    return a * b;
}
module.exports = multiply;
